2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshoppers-spending-less-retailers-brands-cutting-prices-economy-explained-why-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumer%20spending%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ominous%20sign%2C%20but%20far%20from%20a%20guarantee%20that%20a%20recession%20is%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20they're%20any%20less%20fascinating%20to%20examine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20nine%20less%20conventional%20signs%20to%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c3340aa3-b62c-4a25-8d00-154441883ada%5C%22%3ESnack%20index%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20some%20evidence%20that%20people%20buy%20fewer%20snacks%20%E2%80%94%20and%20other%20types%20of%20food%20%E2%80%94%20when%20a%20recession%20hits.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC8084260%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOne%20review%20of%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20the%20Great%20Recession%20of%202008%20reduced%20the%20consumption%20of%20snacks%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20foods%20from%20fast%20food%20to%20fresh%20produce%2C%20for%20instance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20consumers%20are%20snacking%20less%2C%20and%20it%20may%20have%20to%20do%20with%20uncertainty%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Mills%2C%20the%20company%20that%20makes%20Chex%20Mix%20and%20Nature%20Valley%20granola%20bars%2C%20reported%20last%20week%20that%20its%20net%20sales%20fell%205%25%20during%20its%20third%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20just%20human%20snacks%20that%20took%20a%20hit%2C%20CEO%20Jeff%20Harmening%20said%20on%20the%20company's%20earnings%20call.%20General%20Mills'%20sales%20of%20pet%20snacks%20were%20also%20down%2C%20he%20told%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20view%20is%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20has%20to%20do%20with%20consumer%20confidence%2C%26quot%3B%20Harmening%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22123bb7ab-6836-4ebc-a2d3-ccb61a9a7e05%5C%22%3EMini%20alcohol%20bottle%20indicator%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20theory%20says%20that%20shoppers%20cut%20back%20on%20alcohol%20purchases%20when%20they're%20concerned%20about%20finances%20and%20the%20economy.%20Instead%20of%20buying%20full%20bottles%20of%20booze%2C%20they%20go%20for%20the%20small%20ones%20you%20find%20on%20airplanes%20or%20in%20hotel%20mini-bars%2C%20the%20theory%20goes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown-Forman%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20Jack%20Daniels%20whiskey%20and%20Herradura%20tequila%2C%20has%20said%20that%20consumers%20are%20buying%20more%20of%20the%20small%20bottles%20lately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20small%20sizes%20are%20doing%20well%20is%20more%20because%20of%20the%20cyclical%20inflation%20and%20it's%20a%20consumer%20that's%20pinched%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20Lawson%20Whiting%20said%20during%20an%20earnings%20call%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d8c8283-c450-4e37-baee-f3ef5a18b6ea%5C%22%3ELipstick%20index%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flipstick-index-explained-how-makeup-sales-could-forecast-recession-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecreation%20of%20the%20lipstick%20index%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20widely%20attributed%20to%20Leonard%20Lauder%2C%20one%20of%20the%20billionaire%20heirs%20to%20the%20Est%C3%A9e%20Lauder%20cosmetics%20fortune.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202001%2C%20when%20the%20US%20economy%20was%20in%20the%20throes%20of%20a%20recession%2C%20Lauder%20noticed%20that%20lipstick%20sales%20were%20actually%20rising%2C%20not%20falling.%20Lauder's%20theory%20was%20that%20lipstick%20sales%20and%20the%20health%20of%20the%20economy%20were%20in%20inverse%20proportion%20to%20one%20another%20%E2%80%94%20essentially%2C%20as%20the%20economy%20got%20worse%2C%20lipstick%20sales%20got%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELipstick%20sales%20at%20mass%20retailers%20were%20up%2011%25%20back%20when%20Lauder%20invented%20the%20index%3B%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20cosmetics%20brands%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fbusiness%2F2008%2Fdec%2F22%2Frecession-cosmetics-lipstick%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereported%20a%20sales%20boost%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202008%20as%20the%20US%20headed%20into%20a%20recession%3B%20and%20even%20though%20high%20inflation%20has%20stayed%20a%20constant%20in%20the%20US%20over%20the%20past%20several%20months%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeauty-shoppers-still-spending-big-as-us-consumers-cut-elsewhere-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebeauty%20sales%20have%20boomed%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20lipstick%20probably%20isn't%20a%20reliable%20recession%20indicator%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20times%20when%20cosmetics%20sales%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2Fmakeup-is-seen-taking-over-holiday-beauty-sales.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eboomed%20during%20times%20of%20relative%20economic%20prosperity%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flipstick-sales-increase-expected-after-cdc-lifts-mask-mandate-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edipped%20during%20downturns%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226000d54d-14b1-4a6e-8bc6-298fbf997ed0%5C%22%3EUnderwear%20index%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20men's%20underwear%20index%20was%20probably%20made%20most%20famous%20by%20former%20Federal%20Reserve%20Chair%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2Ftemplates%2Fstory%2Fstory.php%3FstoryId%3D17759341%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAlan%20Greenspan%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20theory%20states%20that%20when%20the%20economy%20worsens%2C%20men%20will%20stop%20buying%20new%20underw