esponses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20year%20since%20then%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20high%20command%20has%20now%20sprung%20a%20surprise%20by%20naming%20Chandrasekhar%20as%20its%20new%20Kerala%20state%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Surprise%20Choice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20no%20means%20was%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20the%20frontrunner.%20Incumbent%20K.%20Surendran%2C%20who%20overstayed%20his%20term%20by%20two%20years%2C%20was%20tipped%20to%20get%20another%20year's%20extension%2C%20until%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20in%202026.%20There%20were%20other%20contenders%20too%2C%20such%20as%20firebrand%20Sobha%20Surendran%20and%20veteran%20MT%20Ramesh.%20Even%20conventional%20wisdom%20suggested%20that%20social%20engineering%20compulsions%20would%20go%20against%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20a%20Nair%20hailing%20from%20Thrissur.%20With%20the%20two%20Malayalis%20in%20Modi's%20third%20ministry%20being%20a%20Nair%20and%20a%20Syrian%20Christian%E2%80%94Suresh%20Gopi%20and%20George%20Kurian%E2%80%94an%20Ezhava%2FHindu%20OBC%20candidate%20would've%20been%20the%20more%20practical%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20high%20command%20had%20enough%20reasons%20to%20pick%20Chandrasekhar.%C2%A0The%20BJP%20in%20Kerala%20is%20a%20divided%20house%20with%20multiple%20factions%2C%20and%20none%20of%20the%20frontrunners%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20function%20smoothly%20on%20account%20of%20internal%20dissension.%20Even%20K.%20Surendran's%20five-year%20term%20was%20marred%20by%20friction%20with%20the%20PK%20Krishnadas-led%20faction%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20running%20feud%20with%20Sobha%20Surendran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leadership%20reckons%20that%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20can%20carry%20all%20the%20factions%20together.%20He%20is%20not%20a%20natural%20politician%2C%20but%20the%20central%20leadership%20deems%20that%20this%20very%20characteristic%20will%20become%20Chandrasekhar's%20USP.%20It%20is%20very%20much%20a%20repetition%20of%20the%20'K.%20Annamalai'%20experiment%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAcceptable%20To%20All%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%2C%20Chandrasekhar's%20acceptability%20cuts%20across%20factions.%20But%20there%20are%20various%20other%20considerations%20at%20play.%20For%20all%20the%20gains%20it%20made%20elsewhere%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20hardly%20had%20any%20electoral%20impact%20in%20Kerala%2C%20despite%20a%20steady%20rise%20in%20vote%20share.%20Even%20after%20faring%20reasonably%20well%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20cornering%20nearly%2020%25%20votes%20and%20Suresh%20Gopi's%20win%20from%20Thrissur%2C%20it%20did%20badly%20in%20the%20Palakkad%20by-election%20last%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20loss%20probably%20put%20paid%20to%20Surendran's%20hopes%20to%20stay%20on%20until%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20as%20he%20had%20turned%20the%20issue%20into%20a%20battle%20of%20prestige.%20The%20central%20leadership%20also%20cannot%20quite%20understand%20why%20the%20BJP%20does%20so%20poorly%20in%20a%20state%20where%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20has%20the%20second-largest%20network%20of%20%3Cem%3Eshakhas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(branches)%20in%20the%20country.%20For%20long%2C%20the%20RSS%20in%20Kerala%20had%20been%20deeply%20involved%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20state%20BJP%2C%20though%20the%20party's%20ideological%20mentor%20has%20taken%20a%20backseat%20in%20recent%20times.%20This%20was%20meant%20to%20afford%20more%20autonomy%20to%20the%20state%20party%20president%2C%20but%20it%20ultimately%20culminated%20in%20RSS%20organising%20secretary%20K.%20Subash's%20resignation%2C%20with%20the%20Sangh%20not%20naming%20a%20replacement%20in%20his%20stead%20for%20an%20extended%20period.%20Now%2C%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar's%20appointment%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20the%20RSS%20naming%20an%20organising%20secretary%20to%20assist%20the%20new%20president%20in%20his%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20the%20high%20command%20named%20an%20out-of-the-box%20candidate%20as%20state%20president%20was%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202016%20assembly%20polls%2C%20when%20veteran%20Sangh%20leader%20Kummanam%20Rajasekharan%2C%20whose%20hardliner%20image%20and%20association%20with%20the%20Nilakkal%20protests%20of%201982%20had%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20baggage%20for%20the%20party%20in%20the%20past.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECourting%20The%20Middle-Class%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20leadership%20also%20believes%20that%20Chandrasekhar%20can%20cater%20to%20sections%20of%20Kerala's%20aspirational%20middle%20class%20that%20are%20yearning%20for%20change%20and%20are%20unhappy%20with%20both%20the%20ruling%20Left%20government%20and%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Democratic%20Front%20(UDF).%20Since%20Chandrasekhar%20doesn't%20fit%20the%20mould%20of%20a%20regular%20politician%2C%20he%20may%20be%20able%20to%20connect%20better%20with%20this%20class%20and%20some%20increasingly%20%E2%80%98apolitical'%20sections%20of%20voters%20that%20support%2C%20say%2C%20a%20Shashi%20Tharoor.%20In%20many%20ways%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20the%20spirited%20contest%20that%20he%20put%20in%20against%20Tharoor%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20late%20entrant%2C%20that%20may%20have%20propelled%20Chandrasekhar%20to%20the%20coveted%20position%20today.%20Giving%20a%20tough%20fight%20to%20Tharoor%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20left%20wondering%20whether%20Chandrasekhar%20could%20have%20emerged%20victorious%20had%20he%20been%20pencilled%20in%20sooner.%20%E2%80%9CIni%20Karyam%20Nadakkum%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%98Now%20things%20will%20move')%20was%20Chandrasekhar's%20campaign%20slogan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Long%20Journey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20well%20be%20called%20Chandrasekhar's%20second%20coming%20in%20Kerala%20politics.%20Contrary%20to%20what%20many%20may%20believe%2C%20the%20contest%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%20wasn't%20his%20initiation%20in%20state%20politics%2C%20even%20if%20he%20was%20based%20in%20Bengaluru%20until%20then.%20Much%20before%20that%2C%20he%20had%20been%20a%20key%20mediator%20for%20getting%20the%20Bharat%20Dharma%20Jana%20Sena%20(BDJS)%2C%20affiliated%20to%20the%20Ezhava%20community%20outfit%20Sree%20Narayana%20Dharma%20Paripalana%20Yogam%20(SNDP)%2C%20to%20join%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20in%202016.%20That%20is%20when%20Chandrasekhar%20was%20named%20the%20NDA's%20vice-chairman%20for%20Kerala%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Karnataka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%20may%20be%20expected%20to%20act%20as%20a%20bridge%20to%20the%20Christian%20clergy%20and%20cater%20to%20their%20grievances.%20The%20Christian%20community%20in%20Kerala%20has%20traditionally%20stood%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20although%20cracks%20have%20begun%20to%20appear%20in%20recent%20times.%20Chandrasekhar%20may%20be%20expected%20to%20utilise%20issues%20such%20as%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20Munambam%20suburb%20of%20Ernakulam%2C%20where%20some%20600%20LChristian%20and%20Hindu%20families%20are%20protesting%20against%20the%20Waqf%20Board's%20claim%20over%20the%20area.%20Notably%2C%20Chandrasekhar%20was%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20getting%20veteran%20leader%20PC%20George%20to%20merge%20his%20splinter%20party%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Shone%20George%2C%20the%20latter's%20son%2C%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20emerge%20as%20an%20important%20leader%20during%20Chandrasekhar's%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedia%20Man%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20also%20be%20remiss%20not%20to%20mention%20Chandrasekhar's%20ownership%20of%C2%A0%3Ci%3EAsianet%20News%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20which%20has%20consistently%20topped%20BARC%20(Broadcast%20Audience%20Research%20Council)%20ratings%20for%20Malayalam%20news%20channels.%20He%20is%20the%20majority%20shareholder%20of%3Ci%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Ethe%20news%20channel%C2%A0through%20the%20holding%20company%20Jupiter%20Capital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20BJP%20leaders%20think%20that%20with%20the%20channel%20maintaining%20an%20independent%20editorial%20line%20Chandrasekhar's%20business%20interests%20may%20backfire%20on%20him%2C%20that%20could%20be%20a%20thin%20reading%20of%20the%20situation.%20This%20view%20got%20amplified%20recently%20when%20he%20had%20to%20tweet%20an%20apology%20on%20account%20of%20the%20channel's%20alleged%20slighting%20of%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20on%20a%20news%20show.%20The%20uber-enthusiastic%20coverage%20of%20Chandrasekhar's%20appointment%20as%20state%20BJP%20president%20was%20also%20duly%20noted%20by%20its%20viewers%2C%20sparking%20discussions%20whether%20it%20portended%20a%20change%20of%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20being%20the%20sharp%20businessman%20he%20is%2C%20Chandrasekhar%20may%20well%20understand%20that%20getting%20the%20channel%20to%20adopt%20a%20pro-BJP%20line%20could%20be%20counterproductive%20until%20the%20political%20climate%20in%20the%20state%20turns%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20party.%20He%20can%20always%20choose%20to%20intervene%20whenever%20he%20deems%20fit.%C2%A0In%20any%20case%2C%20as%20a%20politician%2C%20owning%20a%20channel%20has%20its%20perks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrossing%20The%20Threshold%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20state%20BJP%20president%2C%20Chandrasekhar%20will%20be%20expected%20to%20adopt%20a%20hands-on%20approach%20to%20organisational%20affairs.%20The%20three-time%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20is%20known%20to%20be%20short-tempered%20and%20will%20have%20to%20be%20at%20his%20diplomatic%20best%20while%20dealing%20with%20veteran%20state%20leaders.%20He%20will%20also%20be%20expected%20not%20to%20resort%20to%20communal%20statements%E2%80%94as%20he%20has%20sometimes%20done%20in%20the%20past%E2%80%94and%20rise%20above%20them%20to%20make%20a%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20leader%20may%20also%20have%20to%20navigate%20the%20mistakes%20perpetuated%20by%20his%20predecessors.%20Malayalis%2C%20like%20any%20other%20populace%2C%20are%20a%20proud%20people.%20The%20%E2%80%98Kerala-bashing'%20that%20state%20BJP%20leaders%20frequently%20resort%20to%20is%20one%20of%20the%20many%20reasons%20the%20party%20has%20failed%20to%20make%20much%20headway%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrasekhar%20has%20his%20task%20cut%20out%3A%20turn%20the%20BJP%20from%20an%20also-ran%20to%20a%20winning%20horse%20in%20Kerala.%20If%20the%20saffron%20party%20can%20manage%20to%20get%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20total%20vote%20share%E2%80%94it'll%20need%20to%20add%20just%20five%20more%20percentage%20points%20to%20its%20current%20tally%E2%80%94it%20will%20have%20established%20itself%20as%20a%20serious%20player%20in%20Kerala.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Anand%20Kochukudy%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742980260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fedc7tfro_rajeev-chandrasekhar_625x300_26_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-a-technocrat-fix-all-thats-wrong-with-bjp-in-kerala-8014559%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20central%20leadership%20believes%20that%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20can%20cater%20to%20sections%20of%20Kerala's%20aspirational%20middle%20class%20that%20are%20unhappy%20with%20both%20the%20ruling%20Left%20government%20and%20the%20Congress-led%20UDF.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-a-technocrat-fix-all-thats-wrong-with-bjp-in-kerala-8014559%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Kohli%2C%20Dhoni%20facing%20criticism%20after%20Iyer's%20selfless%20act%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%2