mpproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1lp365pd1go.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1lp365pd1go.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20work%20habits%20were%20hurting%20my%20marriage.%20Here%20are%20the%203%20shifts%20I%20made%20that%20increased%20my%20profits%20and%20helped%20my%20relationship.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225787%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Liane%20Agbi%20smiling%20wearing%20a%20black%20suit%20siting%20on%20a%20white%20modern%20sofa.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dcab09b8b41a9673fb4d52%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELiane%20Agbi%20said%20she%20went%20from%20working%20past%20dinnertime%20to%20ending%20her%20day%20at%206%20p.m.%2C%20which%20improved%20her%20business%20and%20her%20relationship%20with%20her%20husband.%3Cp%3EAshley%20Jean%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20entrepreneur%20named%20Liane%20Agbi%20struggled%20with%20balancing%20her%20relationship%20and%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20hired%20extra%20help%2C%20used%20automated%20systems%2C%20and%20made%20her%20husband%20an%20accountability%20partner.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThese%20changes%20revamped%20her%20work-life%20balance%20and%20boosted%20her%20profits%20to%20over%20%24190%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Liane%20Agbi%2C%20a%2034-year-old%20entrepreneur%20in%20Jersey%20City%2C%20New%20Jersey.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20the%20profits%20mentioned%20in%20this%20article%2C%20which%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20launched%20my%20web%20design%20agency%20in%20April%202021%2C%20I%20had%20some%20business%20acumen%2C%20but%20I%20really%20didn't%20understand%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-right-way-to-set-boundaries-with-people-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etimelines%20or%20boundaries%3C%2Fa%3E%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20fianc%C3%A9%2C%20now%20husband%2C%20and%20I%20were%20both%20going%20to%20be%20working%20from%20home%2C%20so%20I%20figured%20we'd%20spend%20so%20much%20more%20time%20together%20and%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20do%20fun%20midday%20activities.%20That%20wasn't%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20days%2C%20I'd%20log%20on%20to%20my%20computer%20around%208%20a.m.%20and%20work%20until%206%20or%207%20p.m.%20After%20having%20dinner%20and%20maybe%20watching%20a%20show%20together%2C%20I'd%20be%20back%20on%20my%20laptop%2C%20falling%20asleep%20on%20the%20couch%20with%20it%20in%20my%20lap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20difficult%20conversation%20with%20my%20husband%20made%20me%20realize%20I%20wasn't%20living%20the%20life%20I%20wanted%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20make%20drastic%20changes%20to%20the%20way%20I%20navigated%20my%20business.%20After%20implementing%20three%20changes%2C%20I%20worked%20less%2C%20my%20relationship%20was%20stronger%2C%20and%20in%20one%20year%20I%20increased%20my%20productivity%20and%20grew%20my%20profits%20to%20%24192%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d941290e-b37b-4186-9206-29808edeab46%5C%22%3EThe%20reality%20of%20entrepreneurship%20was%20not%20how%20I%20imagined%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20time%20passed%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20cutting%20meals%20with%20my%20husband%20shorter%2C%20keeping%20interactions%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bhi%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbye%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20rescheduling%20date%20nights%20in%20favor%20of%20work.%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20shut%20off%20my%20work%20brain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20end%20of%202021%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20had%20just%20gotten%20married%2C%20and%20he%20sat%20me%20down%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconversations-to-have-with-your-partner-before-marriage-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20tough%20conversation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20asked%20me%20if%20the%20way%20I%20was%20operating%2C%20sacrificing%20everything%20for%20my%20business%2C%20was%20the%20vision%20I%20had%20for%20our%20marriage%20and%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20simple%20question%20opened%20my%20eyes%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20my%20current%20lifestyle%20was%20unsustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241d9389f-3ad8-4189-b6ef-22c2fe088cee%5C%22%3ESetting%20boundaries%20with%20my%20work%20schedule%20has%20made%20a%20huge%20difference%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20with%20a%207%20or%208%20p.m.%20cut-off%20time%20for%20work%20and%20moved%20it%20earlier%20as%20I%20got%20more%20comfortable%20disconnecting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENowadays%2C%20I%20don't%20respond%20to%20clients%20after%204%20p.m.%2C%20and%20if%20someone%20tries%20to%20reach%20me%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20they%20might%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgmail-out-of-office%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereceive%20an%20auto-response%3C%2Fa%3E%20stating%20I'm%20out%20of%20the%20office%20and%20will%20get%20back%20to%20them%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20longest%20time%2C%20I%20was%20too%20nervous%20to%20use%20an%20automated%20email%20message%20because%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20signal%20to%20clients%20that%20I%20was%20unresponsive%2C%20but%20this%20change%20has%20brought%20me%20a%20huge%20sense%20of%20relief%20by%20helping%20me%20turn%20off%20my%20work%20brain%20and%20be%20present%20with%20my%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231d49d71-e6a3-4899-be75-6250c1370270%5C%22%3EHiring%20people%20to%20help%20with%20my%20business%20grew%20my%20revenue%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20I%20hired%20a%20%244%2C000%20business%20coach%20for%20a%20seven-week%20program%20to%20help%20me%20create%20workflow%20systems%20for%20my%20emerging%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20lasting%20lesson%20she%20taught%20me%20was%20the%20power%20of%20leveraging%20automation%2C%20such%20as%20email%20scheduling%2C%20