ied%20how%20easy%20an%20online%20business%20can%20be.%20I%20spent%20day%20after%20day%20messaging%20with%20seller%20service%20representatives%20to%20work%20out%20issues%20with%20shipping%2C%20payment%2C%20design%2C%20and%20much%20more.%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-deal-with-stress-burnout-work-mental-health-professional-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estressed%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20almost%20all%20the%20time%2C%20desperate%20to%20do%20a%20great%20job%20and%20make%20my%20customers%20happy%2C%20while%20also%20trying%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20my%20family's%20needs%20and%20working%20as%20a%20freelance%20writer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229cf815e6-927a-4919-9fb3-f2d9227e849f%5C%22%3EThe%20business%20was%20moderately%20successful%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20maintain%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20starting%20my%20online%20business%2C%20I%20already%20had%20a%20loyal%20and%20moderate%20social%20media%20following.%20The%20problem%20for%20me%20wasn't%20getting%20exposure%20and%20selling%20shirts.%20My%20struggle%20was%20all%20of%20the%20other%20tasks%2C%20such%20as%20products%20lost%20in%20the%20mail%20and%20constant%20website%20updates%2C%20that%20come%20with%20running%20an%20online%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20small%20issues%20became%20all-consuming.%20I%20sold%20some%20wonderful%20breast%20cancer%20awareness%20and%20racial%20equity%20tees%20that%20customers%20loved%2C%20with%20more%20designs%20in%20the%20works.%20Yet%2C%20there%20was%20nothing%20passive%20about%20getting%20the%20products%20made%20and%20sent%20to%20customers%20in%20a%20timely%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20my%20online%20T-shirt%20business%20up%20and%20running%20for%20only%20about%20three%20months%2C%20bringing%20in%20a%20little%20under%20%241%2C000.%20Some%20may%20say%20I%20gave%20up%20too%20easily%2C%20especially%20since%20I%20had%20some%20success%20early%20on.%20But%20the%20videos%20I%20had%20watched%20promised%20that%20once%20everything%20was%20up%20and%20running%2C%20the%20business%20would%20be%20passive%20in%20both%20effort%20and%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20truth%20is%2C%20the%20demands%20of%20selling%20tees%20online%20increased%20over%20time%2C%20and%20there%20was%20nothing%20hands-off%20about%20the%20experience.%20The%20business%20consumed%20my%20time%20and%20energy%20until%20I%20opted%20to%20close%20up%20shop.%20I'm%20both%20pleased%20and%20disappointed%20in%20my%20decision.%20I%20still%20have%20so%20many%20ideas%20for%20tees%2C%20but%20the%20lack%20of%20profit%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20workload%20simply%20doesn't%20make%20sense.%20My%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-prioritizing-time-is-more-valuable-than-saving-money-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etime%20is%20valuable%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20this%20endeavor%20just%20wasn't%20worthwhile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaking-passive-income-selling-tees-online-not-easy-side-hustle-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742979902000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67daba68585f1dff88b28eba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaking-passive-income-selling-tees-online-not-easy-side-hustle-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Making%20passive%20income%20selling%20T-shirts%20online%20wasn't%20as%20simple%20as%20social%20media%20posts%20said%20it%20would%20be.%20Instead%2C%20I%20was%20constantly%20stressed%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Rachel%20Garlinghouse)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaking-passive-income-selling-tees-online-not-easy-side-hustle-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata%20Group%20Now%20Tesla's%20Global%20Supplier%2C%20Eyes%20Role%20In%20India%20Expansion%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMultinational%20conglomerate%20Tata%20Group%20has%20reportedly%20become%20a%20global%20supplier%20of%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk's%20electric%20vehicle%20(EV)%20company%20Tesla.%20Several%20Tata%20firms%2C%20including%20Tata%20Technologies%2C%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%20(TCS)%2C%20Tata%20AutoComp%2C%20and%20Tata%20Electronics%2C%20are%20now%20part%20of%20Tesla's%20supply%20chain%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20The%20Economic%20Times%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Frenewables%2Ftata-group-partners-with-tesla-a-new-era-for-indian-electric-vehicle-supply-chains%2Farticleshow%2F119270573.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EET%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20report%2C%20these%20Tata%20companies%20have%20already%20signed%20global%20agreements%20with%20the%20automaker%20as%20essential%20partners%20and%20are%20providing%20crucial%20components%20and%20services%20to%20Tesla%2C%20which%20represents%20approximately%20half%20of%20the%20global%20automotive%20industry's%20market%20value.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20firms%20contributed%20to%20the%20approximately%20%24%202%20billion%20worth%20of%20Indian%20supplies--%20including%20castings%2C%20forgings%2C%20electronics%2C%20and%20fabrication%20parts--%20to%20the%20American%20automaker%20in%20FY24.%20%C2%A0With%20the%20EV%20maker%20looking%20to%20diversify%20its%20supply%20chain%2C%20its%20sourcing%20from%20India%20is%20expected%20to%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tata%20group%20is%20now%20positioning%20itself%20for%20expanded%20opportunities%20and%20growing%20further%2C%20especially%20if%20Tesla%20sets%20up%20a%20manufacturing%20unit%20in%20India.%20Billionaire%20Musk's%20company%20has%20also%20initiated%20conversations%20with%20existing%20Indian%20suppliers%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20establishing%20facilities%20near%20their%20manufacturing%20centres%20to%20enhance%20the%20supply%20ecosystem%2C%20the%20ET%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTesla%20is%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20readying%20the%20supplier%20base%20in%20India...We%20are%20very%20sure%20that%20once%20Tesla%20starts%20manufacturing%20here%2C%20Indian%20suppliers%20will%20benefit%20from%20sourcing%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20top%20industry%20source%20told%20ET%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20Tesla's%20Senior%20procurement%20executives%20have%20been%20meeting%20with%20numerous%20current%20suppliers%20about%20manufacturing%20specific%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETesla's%20India%20Expansion%20Plans%20In%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Tesla%20is%20evaluating%20manufacturing%20opportunities%20in%20India%20and%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20government%20incentives%2C%20tax%20benefits%2C%20and%20potential%20duty%20waivers%20before%20making%20a%20final%20decision.%20While%20the%20EV%20maker%20has%20not%20confirmed%20its%20manufacturing%20plans%2C%20reports%20indicate%20that%20it%20is%20in%20talks%20with%20several%20states%2C%20including%20Rajasthan%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Telangana%2C%20to%20explore%20options%20for%20setting%20up%20a%20production%20facility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Tesla%20moves%20ahead%20with%20its%20India%20plans%2C%20Tata's%20role%20in%20its%20supply%20chain%20could%20grow%20even%20further.%20The%20ET%20report%20said%20the%20American%20company%20has%20strict%20non-disclosure%20agreements%20with%20its%20suppliers%2C%20which%20prevent%20them%20from%20revealing%20details%20about%20their%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20sources%20told%20ET%20that%20Tesla%20also%20intends%20to%20procure%20various%20components%20from%20suppliers%20outside%20China%20and%20Taiwan%2C%20including%20wiring%20harnesses%2C%20electric%20motors%2C%20gearboxes%2C%20forged%20components%2C%20castings%2C%20sheet%20metal%2C%20sophisticated%20electronics%2C%20suspension%20systems%2C%20electric%20powertrains%2C%20and%20ball%20and%20ceramic%20bearings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETata%20Group's%20Supplies%20To%20Tesla%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETata%20AutoComp%20provides%20specialised%20EV%20engineering%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETata%20Technologies%20delivers%20comprehensive%20product%20lifecycle%20management%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETCS%20supplies%20circuit-board%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETata%20Electronics%20provides%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20financial%20daily%20reported%20that%20while%20these%20companies%20within%20the%20Tata%20ecosystem%20maintain%20their%20current%20global%20supply%20arrangements%2C%20their%20future%20strategic%20decisions%20may%20be%20influenced%20by%20Tesla's%20ultimate%20decision%20regarding%20local%20manufacturing%20or%20contract%20manufacturing%20for%20the%20Indian%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20EV%20maker%20has%20established%20partnerships%20with%20numerous%20Indian%20manufacturers%2C%20including%20prominent%20names%20such%20as%20Samvardhana%20Motherson%2C%20Suprajit%20Engineering%2C%20Sona%20BLW%20Precision%20Forgings%2C%20Varroc%20Engineering%2C%20Bharat%20Forge%2C%20and%20Sandhar%20Technologies%2C%20for%20sourcing%20vital%20components%2C%20but%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20source%20essential%20vehicle%20control%20components%20from%20Tata%20Electronics%2C%20including%20printed%20circuit%20board%20assemblies%20for%20Tesla's%20battery%20management%20systems%2C%20motor%20controller%20units%20and%20door%20control%20mechanism%2C%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742979780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F2eo3sfs_tata-tesla_625x300_26_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftata-group-now-teslas-global-supplier-eyes-role-in-india-expansion-report-8014515%22%2