r%20%24175M.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20says%20she%20falsely%20claimed%20to%20have%20marketing%20data%20for%20more%20than%204%20million%20Frank%20account%20holders.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDaylong%20closing%20arguments%20are%20scheduled%20to%20begin%20at%209%20a.m.%20Wednesday%20in%20the%20Charlie%20Javice%20fraud%20trial%20in%20New%20York%20%E2%80%94%20and%20one%20word%20will%20likely%20play%20a%20starring%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20pivotal%20word%20is%20%26quot%3Buser.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20prosecutors%20say%20that%20almost%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20Javice%20defrauded%20the%20nation's%20largest%20bank%2C%20JPMorgan%20Chase%2C%20out%20of%20%24175%20million%2C%20the%20price%20the%20bank%20paid%20for%20her%20financial%20aid%20website%2C%20Frank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20indictment%2C%20prosecutors%20alleged%20that%20Javice%20tricked%20bank%20executives%20into%20thinking%20that%20if%20they%20purchased%20Frank%2C%20they%20would%20become%20the%20new%20owners%20of%20the%20names%2C%20emails%2C%20and%20addresses%20of%20more%20than%204%20million%20Frank%20%3Cem%3Eusers%3C%2Fem%3E.%20These%20users%20were%20students%20at%20the%20start%20of%20their%20financial%20journeys%2C%20to%20whom%20JPMorgan%20could%20market%20checking%20accounts%20and%20credit%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20five%20weeks%20of%20testimony%2C%20lawyers%20for%20Javice%20have%20sought%20to%20show%20that%20this%20is%20not%20what%20she%20had%20meant%20by%20%3Cem%3Eusers%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20her%20lawyers%20say%2C%20she%20told%20the%20bank%20that%204%20million%20people%20had%20merely%20visited%20the%20website%20and%20clicked%20around%20a%20bit%2C%20a%20number%20supported%20by%20Google%20Analytics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrank%20only%20ever%20collected%20personal%20identifying%20data%20for%20300%2C000%20account%20holders%2C%20not%204%20million%2C%20both%20sides%20agree%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fact%20the%20bank%20says%20they%20only%20discovered%20months%20after%20the%20merger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20a%20central%20dispute%20in%20front%20of%20jurors%20%E2%80%94%20as%20they%20listen%20to%20closing%20arguments%20by%20attorneys%20for%20the%20government%2C%20for%20Javice%2C%20and%20for%20her%20top%20lieutenant-turned-co-defendant%20Olivier%20Amar%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20this%3A%20How%20did%20Javice%2C%2032%2C%20and%20Amar%2C%2050%2C%20define%20%26quot%3Buser%26quot%3B%20in%20negotiations%20with%20JPMorgan%3F%20As%20a%20nameless%20clicker%3F%20Or%20as%20a%20potential%20Chase%20customer%20whom%20the%20bank%20could%20email%20and%20text%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20District%20Judge%20Alvin%20Hellerstein%20raised%20this%20question%20in%20court%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20part%20of%20his%20preparation%20for%20instructing%20the%20jury%20on%20the%20law%20before%20deliberations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20about%20the%20argument%20that%20by%20telling%20Chase%20that%20'We%20have%204.25%20million%20users%2C'%20that%20they%20were%20telling%20the%20truth%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20Georgia%20Kostopoulos%2C%20an%20assistant%20US%20attorney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20lie%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prosecutor%20quickly%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20have%20a%20number%20exactly%20the%20same%20as%20the%20number%20of%20users%20that%20visited%20the%20website%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20pushed%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Google%20Analytics%20total.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20they're%20called%20%3Cem%3Eusers%3C%2Fem%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKostopoulos%20countered%20that%20both%20Javice%20and%20Amar%20were%20present%20at%20a%20July%2021%2C%202021%2C%20meeting%20where%20Javice%20assured%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20that%20a%20user%20was%20someone%20who%20had%20provided%20Frank%20with%20their%20name%20and%20other%20personal%20identifying%20information%20as%20part%20of%20signing%20up%20for%20a%20website%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20was%20also%20told%20at%20that%20meeting%20that%20at%20least%20half%20of%20these%204%20million%20users%20had%20used%20their%20Frank%20account%20to%20complete%20a%20Free%20Application%20for%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%2C%20or%20FAFSA%2C%20the%20federal%20prosecutor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20trial%20testimony%2C%20filling%20out%20a%20FAFSA%20would%20mean%20these%20users%20gave%20Frank%20their%20Social%20Security%20numbers%20and%20other%20valuable%20personal%20information%2C%20such%20as%20their%20income%20and%20savings%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20has%20limited%20closing%20arguments%20to%20two%20hours%20per%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20scheduled%20to%20present%20its%20arguments%20first%2C%20followed%20by%20Javice's.%20After%20lunch%2C%20jurors%20will%20hear%20arguments%20on%20behalf%20of%20Amar%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20brief%20rebuttal%20statement%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20co-defendants%20are%20charged%20with%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20wire%20and%20bank%20fraud%2C%20along%20with%20separate%20counts%20of%20wire%2C%20bank%2C%20and%20securities%20fraud.%20They%20face%20potential%20maximum%20sentences%20of%2030%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-trial-closings-one-word-will-play-starring-role-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742979662000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e34046b8b41a9673fbb0dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-trial-closings-one-word-will-play-starring-role-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prosectors%20say%20the%20Frank%20founder%20assured%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20that%20the%20financial%20aid%20website%20had%204.25M%20users.%20Just%20what%20she%20meant%20by%20user%20is%20hotly%20disputed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-trial-closings-one-word-will-play-starring-role-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gold%20is%20the%20new%20Trump%20trade%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20for%20all%20the%20wrong%20reasons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trump%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20of%20the%20white%20house%20signing%20executive%20orders%2C%20including%20tariffs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a11cf6eb4be2fff9a34f1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrumps%20tariffs%20cause%20stock%20market%20drop.%20Here's%20how%20to%20protect%20your%20portfolio%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGold%20is%20shining%2C%20though%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20may%20not%20claim%20bragging%20rights.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20yellow%20metal%20has%20taken%20off%20as%20investors%20flock%20to%20the%20safe%20haven%20asset%20during%20unrest.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20why%20most%20strategists%20believe%20the%20generational%20rally%20can%20continue.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fgold-price-today-trump-trade-war-tariffs-safe-haven-markets-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egold%20rush%3C%2Fa%3E%20early%20in%20Donald%20Trump's%20second%20term.%20But%20while%20the%20president%20may%20be%20responsible%20for%20the%20yellow%20metal's%20record%20rally%2C%20don't%20expect%20him%20to%20take%20a%20victory%20lap%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20crave%20certainty%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-trump-tariffs-stock-market-outlook-selloff-strategy-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echaotic%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20that's%20devoid%20of%20it%20due%20to%20Trump's%20policy%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlobal%20trade%20relations%20are%20strained%20as%20the%20US%20initiated%20tariff%20plans%20that%20seem%20to%20shift%20by%20the%20day.%20Policy%20uncertainty%20is%20the%20new%20status%20quo%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-escalates-trade-war-canada-increases-tarrifs-aluminum-steel-cars-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrade%20wars%20can't%20be%20ruled%20out%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Businesses%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-consumer-confidence-corporate-earnings-outlook-risk-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumers%20may%20cut%20back%20on%20spending%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20continued%20economic%20growth%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20sure%20bet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20anxieties%20have%20helped%20fuel%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20surges%20ever%20for%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20oldest%20investments.%20Gold%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20stable%2C%20has%20soared%20from%20just%20over%20%242%2C000%20to%20north%20of%20%243%2C000%20in%20a%20little%20over%20a%20year.%20The%20yellow%20metal%20has%20also%20soared%20by%20double-digits%20since%20Trump%20took%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20geopolitical%20concerns%20that%20made%20gold%20go%20up%20significantly%20in%20the%20last%20six%20months%20are%20still%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mukarram%20Mawjood%2C%20the%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20Blackstone%20Commodity%20Group%2C%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPat%20Kennedy%20wasn't%20surprised%20that%20gold%20caught%20fire%2C%20and%20he%20expects%20it%20to%20vault%2015%25%20to%2020%25%20per%20year%20through%202030%20due%20to%20geopolitical%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20combine%20that%20with%20inflation%20hitting%20a%2040-year%20high%2C%20and%20then%20the%20national%20debt%20really%20getting%20completely%20out%20of%20control%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20where%20gold%20shines%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kennedy%2C%20the%20founding%20partner%20of%20AllSource%20Investment%20Management%2C%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222019ffd8-0d77-4679-b342-070b0bbb37d6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20high%20can%20gold%20go%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20record%20gold%20rally%20is%20well%20supported.%20Bank%20of%20America%20found%20there%20was%20%2410.6%20billion%20in%20inflows%20to%20the%20metal%20from%20mid-February%20to%20mid-March%20%E2%80%94%20the%20most%20ever%20recorded%20in%20a%20four-week%20span.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221606%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gold%20inflows%20BofA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e30b52b8b41a9673fbabc3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22942%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20striking%20is%20that%2058%25%20of%20fund%20managers%20surveyed%20by%20BofA%20said%20the%20precious%20metal%20was%20the%20safest%20asset%20if%20there%20was%20an%20all-out%20trade%20war.%20No%20other%20investment%20even%20got%20above%2016%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221432%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gold%20during%20trade%20war%20BofA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e30b6669253ccddf9a4569%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22886%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20strategists%20and%20investment%20chiefs%20that%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20for%20this%20story%20agree%3A%20gold%20is%20the%20place%20to%20be%20in%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-trading-hedging-strategy-changes-increased-volatility-cme-group-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighly%20volatile%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20next%20four%20years%20%E2%80%94%20however%20long%20we're%20in%20this%20policy%20regime%20%E2%80%94%20we%20think%20that%20it%20is%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20pay%20benefits%20to%20have%20that%20element%20of%20diversification%2C%26quot%3B%20Wayne%20Gordon%2C%20an%20investment%20chief%20at%20UBS%20Global%20Wealth%20Management%2C%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20just%20unrest%20caused%20by%20Trump's%20desire%20to%20reshape%20global%20trade%20policy%20that's%20lifting%20gold.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20bullion's%20gains%20came%20before%20the%202024%20US%20election.%20Gold%20actually%20took%20a%20breather%20once%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20Trump%20won%20and%20didn't%20take%20off%20again%20until%20tariff%20talk%20revved%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20seeing%20a%20duality%20here%20where%20this%20last%20leg%20is%20probably%20more%20financial%20flows%20for%20risk%20hedges%20and%20tail%20hedges%2C%20while%20the%20first%20half%20was%20a%20continuation%20of%20the%202024%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aakash%20Doshi%2C%20the%20head%20of%20gold%20strategy%20at%20State%20Street%20Global%20Advisors%2C%20who%20thinks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ssga.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Findividual%2Finsights%2Fcould-gold-etf-inflows-spur-record-gold-prices-in-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egold%20will%20continue%20to%20climb%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20several%20commentators%20said%20gold%20is%20increasingly%20attractive%20since%20there's%20a%20renewed%20focus%20on%20long-standing%20issues%2C%20like%20how%20the%20US's%20deficit%20spending%20is%20fueling%20its%20immense%20national%20debt.%20The%20US%20government%20has%20a%20seemingly%20insurmountable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usdebtclock.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2436.6%20trillion%20in%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20gives%20it%20an%20incentive%20to%20let%20inflation%20run%20hot%20so%20lower%20real%20dollar%20values%20make%20the%20burden%20more%20manageable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221711%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gold%20vs%20national%20debt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e30bce69253ccddf9a4578%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22754%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20price%20of%20gold%20(light%20blue)%20has%20steadily%20risen%20in%20the%20last%20three%20decades%20and%20is%20correlated%20with%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20US%20national%20debt.%20Both%20figures%20are%20indexed%20to%20100%20as%20of%20April%201%2C%201993.%3Cp%3Eabrdn%20(Aberdeen%20Investments)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20theory%20is%20that%20the%20dollar%20is%20worth%20less%20with%20the%20more%20debt%20that's%20issued%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Robert%20Minter%2C%20the%20director%20of%20ETF%20investment%20strategy%20at%20Aberdeen%20Investments.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20not%20so%20much%20that%20gold%20is%20rising%2C%20it's%20that%20the%20dollar%20is%20falling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdd%20that%20to%20the%20sanctions%20that%20the%20US%20has%20put%20on%20its%20enemies%2C%20like%20Russia%20after%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20it%20makes%20sense%20why%20rival%20governments%20want%20a%20currency%20that%20can't%20be%20controlled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20who's%20sitting%20in%20a%20central%20bank%20really%20thinks%20the%20US%20has%20their%20interests%20in%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20David%20Miller%2C%20the%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20Catalyst%20Funds.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it%20just%20makes%20a%20lot%20of%20sense%20that%20gold%20would%20be%20a%20better%20reserve%20asset%20for%20central%20banks%20of%20non-aligned%20countries%20than%20dollars%20would.%20These%20people%20didn't%20necessarily%20want%20the%20dollar%20as%20their%20reserve%20asset%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMinter%20agreed%20that%20other%20countries%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20beholden%20to%20the%20US%2C%20especially%20if%20its%20leader%20is%20openly%20hostile%20in%20trade%20negotiations.%20That's%20why%20he%20predicted%20that%20global%20central%20banks%20will%20keep%20loading%20up%20on%20gold%2C%20and%20he%20expects%20that%20retail%20investors%20will%20follow%20suit%2C%20in%20part%20through%20ETFs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e4c4041-b28c-4ac1-90eb-75fc72a112c8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20bet%20on%20a%20gold%20boom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20has%20already%20enjoyed%20a%20mammoth%20run%2C%20but%20observers%20believe%20it%20still%20has%20more%20upside%20as%20supply%20stays%20tempered%20and%20demand%20surges%20due%20to%20geopolitical%20and%20economic%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they're%20right%2C%20investors%20could%20get%20access%20to%20the%20yellow%20metal%20by%20buying%20bars%20directly%2C%20adding%20indirect%20exposure%20with%20funds%20that%20track%20it%2C%20targeting%20gold%20miners%2C%20or%20a%20combination%20of%20the%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20those%20options%2C%20the%20consensus%20is%20that%20gold%20mining%20stocks%20are%20the%20shakiest%20proposition.%20Leading%20firms%20like%20Newmont%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnem-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENEM%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20Barrick%20Gold%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fgold-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGOLD%3C%2Fa%3E)%20have%20woefully%20trailed%20gold%20and%20are%20nowhere%20near%20their%20record%20highs%2C%20even%20though%20Minter%20said%20miners%20may%20deliver%20some%20of%20the%20best%20margins%20in%20a%20generation.%20Doshi%20from%20State%20Street%20said%20when%20gold%20miners%20outperform%2C%20it's%20usually%20not%20for%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20better%20to%20own%20gold%20directly%20or%20buy%20a%20fund%20that%20does%2C%20Gordon%20from%20UBS%20said.%20He%20likes%20having%205%25%20of%20one's%20assets%20in%20gold%20as%20a%20baseline%2C%20though%20that%20can%20change%20based%20on%20investors'%20goals%20and%20risk%20tolerance%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20market%20backdrop.%20Gordon%20takes%20a%20tactical%20approach%20to%20gold%20where%20the%20position%20can%20be%20bought%20and%20sold%20as%20needed%20instead%20of%20having%20a%20set-it-and-forget-it%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20is%20proven%20to%20systematically%20beat%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20during%20downturns%2C%20Gordon%20said.%20However%2C%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20to%20see%20the%20asset%20initially%20sell%20off%20as%20investors%20use%20its%20relative%20stability%20to%20add%20to%20stocks%20that%20crater%2C%20which%20is%20what%20happened%20five%20years%20ago%20during%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20client%20is%20holding%20gold%2C%20I%20want%20him%20to%20have%20the%20full%20benefits%20of%20holding%20gold%3A%20the%20diversification%2C%20but%20also%20the%20ability%20to%20liquidate%20that%20gold%20in%20a%20highly%20liquid%20market%20at%20any%20time%20of%20his%20choosing%20to%20raise%20cash%20to%20be%20able%20to%20meet%20needs%20that%20he%20might%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Gordon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20still%2C%20not%20everyone%20is%20optimistic%20about%20gold%20after%20its%20massive%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Mawjood%20from%20Blackstone%20Commodity%20Group%20said%20he%20was%20highly%20bullish%20about%20the%20yellow%20metal%20last%20year%2C%20he's%20skeptical%20about%20gold%20in%20the%20near%20term%2C%20considering%20how%20far%20it%20has%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investment%20chief%20agrees%20with%20bulls'%20thesis%20that%20gold%20is%20a%20good%20hedge%20against%20geopolitical%20risk%2C%20though%20he%20said%20he%20started%20scaling%20out%20of%20gold%20at%20the%20%242%2C600%20and%20%242%2C700%20mark%20since%20he's%20wary%20of%20how%20quickly%20it%20rallied.%20He's%20fine%20with%20losing%20a%20bit%20of%20upside%20if%20it%20saves%20him%20from%20buying%20at%20the%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone's%20so%20bullish%2C%26quot%3B%20Mawjood%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20probably%20the%20reason%20why%20we%20have%20to%20be%20more%20cautious.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-record-rally-trump-tariffs-trade-war-uncertainty-investing-strategy-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742979601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e30aabb8b41a9673fbabab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-record-rally-trump-tariffs-trade-war-uncertainty-investing-strategy-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gold%20is%20shining%20due%20to%20uncertainty%20under%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20and%20most%20strategists%20think%20the%20record%20rally%20still%20has%20room%20to%20run.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jfaris%40businessinsider.com%20(James%20Faris)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A72%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-record-rally-trump-tariffs-trade-war-uncertainty-investing-strategy-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20a%20decades-old%20software%20company%20hitching%20a%20ride%20on%20the%20Nvidia%20rocket%20ship%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226385%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20dressed%20in%20black%20clothes%20and%20a%20black%20leather%20jacket%20satnds%20in%20front%20of%20a%20large%20screen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e3103a63d72727e19838b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223932%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20during%20his%20keynote%20address%20at%20the%20GTC%20AI%20Conference%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20California%2C%20on%20March%2018%2C%202025.%3Cp%3EOSH%20EDELSON%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20AI%20boom%20is%20changing%20the%20trajectory%20of%20decades-old%20computing%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDDN%2C%20known%20in%20the%20supercomputing%20field%2C%20now%20offers%20crucial%20data%20storage%20for%20AI%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20recently%20raised%20%24300%20million%20from%20Blackstone%20at%20a%20%245%20billion%20valuation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Nvidia%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-ai-factory-tokens-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20gave%20his%20keynote%20address%20at%20the%20company's%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gtc-2025-ceo-jensen-huang-ai-landscape-san-jose-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGTC%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20an%20audience%20of%20roughly%2017%2C000%20people%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20California%2C%20last%20week%2C%20dozens%20of%20companies%20sat%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20their%20seats%20to%20find%20out%20if%20they'd%20get%20a%20mention.%20Some%20had%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20slides%20ahead%20of%20time%2C%20but%20no%20one%20knew%20for%20certain%20until%20the%20words%20came%20out%20of%20Huang's%20mouth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDataDirect%20Networks%2C%20or%20DDN%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20lucky%20ones%20to%20leave%20the%20arena%20happy.%20Huang%20named%20the%20company%20alongside%20Dell%2C%20HP%20Enterprise%2C%20Hitachi%2C%20and%20IBM.%20But%20while%20those%20firms%20have%20enjoyed%20broader%20name%20recognition%20in%20the%20tech%20world%20for%20decades%2C%20DDN%20was%20invited%20on%20the%20rocket%20ship%20that%20is%20Nvidia%20just%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20and%20everything%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDDN%20makes%20hardware%2C%20but%20more%20importantly%20software%20that%20allows%20GPU%20users%20to%20access%20their%20stored%20data%20fast.%20It%20cuts%20down%20on%20latency%2C%20which%20is%20the%20industry%20term%20for%20lag%20in%20AI%20systems%20that%20can%20delay%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20answer%20to%20a%20question%20asked%20of%20a%20chatbot%20like%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nvidia%20sells%20%24100%20worth%20of%20GPUs%2C%20DDN's%20opportunity%20is%20%245-10%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20have%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20performance%2C%20reliability%2C%20and%20stability%20to%20extract%20your%20data%20at%20full%20speed%2C%20real-time%2C%20to%20feed%20the%20GPUs%2C%26quot%3B%20Paul%20Bloch%2C%20DDN's%2064-year-old%20President%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20been%20working%20with%20Nvidia%20for%20about%20eight%20years.%20Before%20that%2C%20it%20served%20the%20stable%2C%20but%20much%20smaller%20industry%20of%20supercomputers%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloch%20and%20CEO%20Alex%20Bouzari%20are%20fixtures%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupercomputing-showdown-xai-oracle-meta-microsoft-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupercomputing%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Before%20the%20AI%20boom%2C%20top%20research%20universities%2C%20government%20labs%2C%20and%20the%20oil%20and%20gas%20industry%20knew%20them%20well.%20But%20mainstream%20data%20centers%20didn't%20need%20them.%20They%20do%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20very%20first%20time%2C%20your%20storage%20system%20will%20be%20GPU-accelerated%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%20at%20GTC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222557%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20a%20blue%20suit%20and%20grey%20shirt%20with%20short%2Cwhite%20hair%20and%20glasses%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20an%20orange%2C%20red%2C%20and%20grey%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e317b863d72727e1983a3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221436%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDDN%20President%20and%20Cofounder%20Paul%20Bloch%3Cp%3EDDN%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20data%20sets%20grow%20larger%20and%20AI%20is%20used%20at%20scale%20for%20data-heavy%20applications%20like%20real-time%20video%2C%20Bloch%20can%20see%20a%20day%20when%20the%20company%20scales%20independently%20of%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20a%20sudden%20it's%20much%20easier%20to%20deliver%20the%20value%20in%20AI%20because%20we've%20already%20done%20it%20in%20the%20past%20with%20similar%20market%2C'%20Bloch%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20the%20success%20of%20the%20company%20has%20gone%20exponential.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDDN%20has%20found%20a%20new%20gear%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%20Conversations%2C%20fixes%2C%20new%20features%2C%20and%20deals%20that%20used%20to%20take%20weeks%20and%20months%20now%20take%20days.%20And%20Bloch%20and%20his%20team%20are%20learning%20to%20work%20at%20Jensen%20Huang's%20pace%20%E2%80%94%20what%20he%20calls%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-jensen-huang-job-interview-style-reference-check-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bspeed%20of%20light.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJensen's%20emails%20are%20fantastic.%20They%20are%2010%20words%20or%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloch%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20into%20the%20era%20of%20AI%20has%20taken%20some%20adjustments%2C%20but%20today%2C%20DDN%20and%20its%20competitors%20are%20essential%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gpus-cpus-parallel-computing-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparallel%20computing%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20enables%20AI.%20When%20a%20company%20seeks%20to%20set%20up%20a%20GPU%20cloud%2C%20it%20has%20to%20have%20a%20version%20of%20DDN's%20tech.%20And%20DDN%20is%20part%20of%20Nvidia's%20reference%20architecture%2C%20which%20is%20the%20recommended%20setup%20for%20maximal%20GPU%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20of%20Nvidia's%20customers%20choose%20to%20use%20these%20instructions%2C%20but%20the%20mere%20fact%20has%20brought%20DDN%20new%20customers.%20Hyperscalers%20have%20traditionally%20preferred%20to%20use%20their%20own%20recipes%20of%20parts%20and%20players%20in%20their%20data%20centers%2C%20but%20Bloch%20said%20that%20in%20the%20era%20of%20Nvidia's%20Blackwell%2C%20they%20are%20starting%20to%20come%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20it's%20preparing%20for%20a%20blockbuster%20third%20decade.%20In%20January%2C%20the%20company%20raised%20%24300%20million%20in%20growth%20funding%20from%20Blackstone%20at%20a%20%245%20billion%20valuation%2C%20and%20Bloch%20got%20a%20congratulatory%20email%20from%20Huang%20at%206%3A30%20a.m.%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20announcement%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDDN%20does%20not%20need%20the%20money%2C%20per%20se%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloch%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20profitable.%20We're%20EBITDA%20positive%2C%20we're%20growing%20very%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20he%20wants%2C%20though%2C%20is%20access%20to%20the%20C-suites%20that%20come%20with%20a%20Blackstone%20affiliation.%20DDN%20used%20to%20sell%20through%20researchers%20and%20developers%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%2C%20the%20technology%20was%20so%20niche%20that%20it%20was%20far%20below%20top%20executives'%20notice.%20Now%2C%20AI%20infrastructure%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20expenditures%20a%20company%20can%20make%2C%20and%20decisions%20around%20it%20are%20scrutinized%20at%20the%20highest%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDDN%20has%20received%20acquisition%20offers%20over%20the%20years%2C%20but%20Bloch%20said%20the%20company%20is%20his%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBouzari's%20%26quot%3Blife's%20work%26quot%3B%20and%20they%20stay%20independent%20by%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20control%20freaks%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloch%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20sees%20two%20to%20five%20years%20more%20of%20break-neck%20AI%20infrastructure%20buildout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20even%20sure%20it's%20going%20to%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-partner-ddn-strategic-leap-nvidia-ai-infrastructure-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742979601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22h