r%20synthetic%20opioids%2C%20is%20the%20most%20lethal%20drug%20trafficked%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20has%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20more%20than%2052%2C000%20Americans%20in%2012%20months%20ending%20in%20October%202024%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Annual%20Threat%20Assessment%20(ATA)%20of%20the%20US%20intelligence%20community%20released%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20groups%20%5Btransnational%20criminal%20organisations%20or%20TCOs%5D%20are%20often%20enabled%2C%20both%20directly%20and%20indirectly%2C%20by%20state%20actors%2C%20such%20as%20China%20and%20India%2C%20as%20sources%20of%20precursors%20and%20equipment%20for%20drug%20traffickers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20published%20by%20the%20office%20of%20Tulsi%20Gabbard%2C%20US%20Director%20of%20National%20Intelligence%20(DNI)%2C%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20remains%20the%20primary%20source%20country%20for%20illicit%20fentanyl%20precursor%20chemicals%20and%20pill%20pressing%20equipment%2C%20followed%20by%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20it%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20US%20has%20placed%20India%20on%20the%20same%20level%20as%20China%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20supply%20of%20precursor%20chemicals%20used%20by%20drug%20cartels%20to%20manufacture%20opioids%20like%20fentanyl.%20Last%20year's%20report%20mentioned%20India%20as%20just%20one%20of%20several%20countries%20from%20where%20the%20Mexican%20groups%20were%20sourcing%20chemicals%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Blesser%20extent%26quot%3B.%20It%20had%20identified%20China%20as%20the%20primary%20supplier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20made%20combating%20opioids%20a%20political%20priority%2C%20shaping%20his%20foreign%20policy%20decisions.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Trump%20said%20his%20administration%20would%20not%20rest%20until%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20ended%20the%20fentanyl%20epidemic%20in%20America%20once%20and%20for%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%201%2C%20the%20American%20commander-in-chief%20imposed%20an%20additional%2010%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20China%20for%20failing%20to%20take%20sufficient%20action%20against%20fentanyl%20trafficking.%20He%20also%20levied%2025%20per%20cent%20duties%20on%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20for%20allegedly%20lacking%20adequate%20border%20enforcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Trump%20has%20threatened%20to%20impose%20reciprocal%20duties%20on%20several%20countries%20as%20part%20of%20his%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20set%20to%20take%20effect%20on%20April%202.%20However%2C%20India%20is%20in%20talks%20with%20America%20to%20expedite%20a%20free%20trade%20deal%20that%20could%20help%20it%20avoid%20some%20of%20these%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742973360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F06lqpfng_tulsi-gabbard-bloomberg_625x300_25_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-intel-report-links-india-to-fentanyl-trafficking-amid-trumps-tariff-threats-8013783%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20has%20named%20India%2C%20along%20with%20China%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bstate%20actor%26quot%3B%20in%20enabling%20direct%20and%20indirect%20supply%20of%20precursor%20chemicals%20for%20illicit%20fentanyl%20drug%20production%20by%20criminal%20organisations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-intel-report-links-india-to-fentanyl-trafficking-amid-trumps-tariff-threats-8013783%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Raina%20Acquires%20%E2%80%98King%20Matt%20the%20First%2C%E2%80%99%20Exploring%20the%20Bond%20Between%20Two%20Sisters%2C%20Ahead%20of%20Hot%20Docs%20Premiere%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742973121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp