0%26quot%3BGrabbing%20Breasts%20Not%20Rape%20Attempt%26quot%3B%20Verdict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20a%20%26quot%3Btotal%20lack%20of%20sensitivity%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20paused%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20ruling%20in%20a%20child%20abuse%20case%2C%20in%20which%20the%20judge%20had%20observed%20that%20the%20grabbing%20of%20breast%20and%20pulling%20the%20string%20of%20a%20pyjama%20don't%20amount%20to%20a%20rape%20attempt.%C2%A0The%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20Augustine%20George%20Masih%20said%20it%20was%20pained%20to%20see%20some%20observations%20in%20the%20verdict%20and%20sought%20replies%20from%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20governments%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20pained%20to%20state%20that%20it%20shows%20a%20total%20lack%20of%20sensitivity%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20author%20of%20the%20judgment.%20It%20was%20not%20even%20at%20the%20spur%20of%20the%20moment%20and%20was%20delivered%20four%20months%20after%20reserving%20the%20same.%20Thus%2C%20there%20was%20application%20of%20mind.%20We%20are%20usually%20hesitant%20to%20grant%20stay%20at%20this%20stage.%20But%20since%20observations%20in%20paragraphs%2021%2C%2024%20and%2026%20is%20unknown%20to%20cannons%20of%20law%20and%20shows%20inhuman%20approach%2C%20we%20stay%20the%20observations%20in%20said%20paras%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20ordered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20agreed%20with%20the%20bench%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bsome%20judgments%20contain%20reasons%20for%20staying%20them%26quot%3B.%C2%A0Justice%20Gavai%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20serious%20matter.%20Total%20insensitiveness%20on%20part%20of%20the%20judge.%20This%20was%20at%20the%20stage%20of%20issuing%20summons!%20We%20are%20sorry%20to%20use%20such%20harsh%20words%20against%20the%20judge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20the%20matter%20suo%20motu%20after%20an%20organisation%2C%20'We%20the%20Women%20of%20India'%2C%20flagged%20the%20high%20court%20ruling.%20The%20victim's%20mother%20has%20also%20moved%20an%20appeal%20in%20the%20top%20court%20and%20it%20has%20been%20tagged%20with%20the%20suo%20motu%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%20in%20question%20was%20delivered%20on%20March%2017%20by%20Justice%20Ram%20Manohar%20Narayan%20Mishra%20of%20Allahabad%20High%20Court.%20The%20judge%20was%20hearing%20the%20accused's%20challenge%20to%20a%20lower%20court%20order%20summoning%20them%20under%20Section%20376%20of%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20which%20deals%20with%20rape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...the%20allegation%20against%20accused%20Pawan%20and%20Akash%20is%20that%20they%20grabbed%20the%20breasts%20of%20the%20victim%20and%20Akash%20tried%20to%20bring%20down%20lower%20garment%20of%20the%20victim%20and%20for%20that%20purpose%20they%20had%20broken%20string%20of%20her%20lower%20garments%20and%20tried%20to%20drag%20her%20beneath%20the%20culvert%2C%20but%20due%20to%20intervention%20of%20witnesses%20they%20left%20the%20victim%20and%20fled%20away%20from%20the%20place%20of%20incident.%20This%20fact%20is%20not%20sufficient%20to%20draw%20an%20inference%20that%20the%20accused%20persons%20had%20determined%20to%20commit%20rape%20on%20victim%20as%20apart%20from%20these%20facts%20no%20other%20act%20is%20attributed%20to%20them%20to%20further%20their%20alleged%20desire%20to%20commit%20rape%20on%20the%20victim%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20para%2021%20of%20the%20high%20court%20ruling%2C%20which%20has%20come%20under%20the%20scanner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minor's%20mother%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%20had%20offered%20a%20lift%20to%20her%20daughter%20and%20assured%20to%20drop%20her%20home.%20%26quot%3BThe%20accused%20persons%20had%20stopped%20their%20motorcycle%20on%20muddy%20way%2C%20on%20way%20to%20her%20village%20they%20started%20grabbing%20her%20breasts%20and%20Akash%20dragged%20her%20and%20tried%20to%20take%20her%20beneath%20the%20culvert%20and%20broke%20the%20string%20of%20her%20pyjami.%20The%20witnesses%20Satish%20and%20Bhurey%20who%20were%20coming%20behind%20on%20a%20tractor%20reached%20the%20spot%20on%20hearing%20cries%20of%20her%20daughter.%20The%20accused%20persons%20threatened%20him%20with%20life%20by%20pointing%20a%20country%20made%20pistol%20to%20them%20and%20fled%20away%20from%20the%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20order%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lower%20court%20had%20summoned%20the%20accused%20under%20IPC%20Section%20376%2C%20relating%20to%20rape%2C%20read%20with%20Section%2018%20of%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act.%20Striking%20this%20down%2C%20the%20high%20court%20judge%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20order%20to%20bring%20out%20a%20charge%20of%20attempt%20to%20rape%20the%20prosecution%20must%20establish%20that%20it%20had%20gone%20beyond%20the%20stage%20of%20preparation.%20The%20difference%20between%20preparation%20and%20actual%20attempt%20to%20commit%20an%20offence%20consists%20chiefly%20in%20the%20greater%20degree%20of%20determination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20observations%20drew%20a%20wave%20of%20criticism%2C%20with%20people%20questioning%20if%20attempts%20to%20undress%20a%20girl%20or%20woman%20against%20her%20will%20do%20not%20qualify%20as%20a%20rape%20attempt%2C%20what%20does%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20voices%20that%20flagged%20the%20regressive%20judgment%20was%20senior%20jurist%20Indira%20Jaising%2C%20who%20had%20called%20for%20a%20suo%20motu%20cognizance%20from%20the%20top%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Bela%20Trivedi%20and%20Justice%20Prasanna%20B%20Varale%20had%20earlier%20refused%20to%20entertain%20a%20petition%20challenging%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Rachna%20Tyagi%2C%20who%20appeared%20for%20the%20survivor's%20mother%2C%20told%20the%20media%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20taken%20cognizance%20of%20serious%20observations%20made%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20and%20stayed%20that%20judgment.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20also%20issued%20notice%20to%20the%20Union%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742972220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F7eeetm5_allahabad-high-court-judge-split-_650x400_26_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftop-court-pauses-allahabad-high-courts-grabbing-breasts-not-rape-verdict-8013190%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22nderlining%20a%20%26quot%3Btotal%20lack%20of%20sensitivity%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20paused%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20ruling%20in%20a%20child%20abuse%20case%2C%20in%20which%20the%20judge%20had%20observed%20that%20grabbing%20of%20breast%20and%20pulling%20the%20string%20of%20a%20pyjama%20don't%20amount%20to%20rape%20attempt%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftop-court-pauses-allahabad-high-courts-grabbing-breasts-not-rape-verdict-8013190%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre's%20Scheme%20For%20Pregnant%20Women%20Severely%20Underfunded%3A%20Sonia%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20has%20flagged%20a%20severe%20lack%20of%20funds%20for%20a%20government%20programme%20that%20aims%20to%20provide%20maternity%20benefits%20to%20pregnant%20women.%20Its%20implementation%20under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20(NFSA)%2C%202013%20needs%20Rs%2012%2C000%20crore%2C%20but%20the%20Budget%20for%20the%20upcoming%20financial%20year%20has%20provided%20only%20Rs%202%2C500%20crore%20for%20such%20programmes%2C%20she%20told%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20NFSA%2C%20pregnant%20women%20are%20entitled%20to%20maternity%20benefits%20worth%20Rs%206%2C000%20per%20child%2C%20paid%20in%20two%20instalments.%20The%20benefits%20extend%20to%20the%20second%20child%20if%20it%20is%20a%20girl.%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Matru%20Vandana%20Yojana%20(PMMVY)%2C%20launched%20in%202017%2C%20provides%20Rs%205%2C000%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20an%20analysis%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20said%2068%25%20of%20all%20pregnant%20women%20received%20at%20least%20one%20instalment%20in%202022-23%2C%20but%20the%20proportion%20fell%20drastically%20after%20that.%20%26quot%3BThe%20very%20next%20year%2C%20this%20proportion%20fell%20to%20just%20around%2012%25.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20ask%20the%20Union%20government%20why%20was%20this%20allowed%20to%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Gandhi%2C%20a%20new%20member%20of%20the%20Upper%20House%2C%20said%20that%20under%20the%20NFSA%2C%20the%20full%20implementation%20of%20the%20maternity%20benefits%20requires%20an%20annual%20budget%20of%20around%20Rs%2012%2C000%20crore%2C%20but%20the%20budget%20outlay%20this%20year%20did%20not%20mention%20any%20allocation%20for%20PMMVY%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20that%20the%20(budget)%20documents%20reveal%20that%20there%20is%20a%20programme%20called%20Samarthya%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development.%20This%20has%20five%20components%2C%20of%20which%20PMMVY%20is%20one.%20The%20allocation%20in%202025-26%20for%20Samarthya%20is%20only%20Rs%202%2C521%20crore.%20This%20clearly%20shows%20that%20the%20PMMVY%20is%20severely%20underfunded%2C%20thereby%20violating%20the%20law%20passed%20by%20the%20parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Gandhi%20had%20opted%20out%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20contest%20last%20year%20and%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20Rajasthan.%20She%20is%20among%20the%2027%20Congress%20MPs%20in%20the%20'House%20of%20Elders'.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742972160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvim