es'%20Pune%20factory%20in%202015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20brand%20will%20start%20retailing%20the%20new%20SL680%20-%20with%20a%20top%20speed%20of%20260%20kmph%20-%20from%20January%20next%20year.%20Daniel%20Lescow%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20brand%20has%20released%20a%20quota%20of%20only%20three%20cars%20for%20India%2C%20which%20have%20already%20been%20sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20millennials%20that%20are%20driving%20the%20sales%20of%20Maybach%20up%20in%20India.%20As%20per%20Lescow%2C%20the%20average%20age%20of%20an%20Indian%20customer%20is%20under%2040%20years%20-%2038%2C%20to%20be%20precise%20-%20as%20a%20younger%20profile%20of%20individuals%20are%20more%20into%20the%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20deep%20interest%20in%20the%20brand%2C%20and%20Indian%20customers%20are%20very%20knowledgeable%20about%20the%20products.%20I%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20maturity%20around%20luxury%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Flifestyle%2Ftravel-melbourne-australia-visa-great-ocean-road-7944473%5C%22%3EIn%20Melbourne%3A%20Polka-Dotted%20Trees%20And%20A%20Great%20Ocean%20Drive%20Down%20Australia's%20Second%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Flifestyle%2Fbhutan-travel-amankora-300-year-old-farmhouse-worlds-happiest-country-7974037%5C%22%3EIn%20Bhutan%3A%20A%20Priapic%20Obsession%20And%20Real%20Luxury%20In%20A%20300-Year-Old%20Farmhouse%20In%20The%20World's%20Happiest%20Country%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742968080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fa1chv2ho_maybach_625x300_26_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Flifestyle%2Fluxury-at-an-all-time-high-as-maybach-sold-ten-cars-weekly-in-india-in-2024-8013021%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20luxur