o%20a%20Reuters%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThousands%20Flee%20Homes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDry%2C%20windy%20weather%20has%20hampered%20efforts%20to%20contain%20the%20fires%2C%20with%20the%20government%20taking%20the%20rare%20step%20of%20evacuating%20thousands%20of%20prisoners%20out%20of%20detention%20centres%20in%20affected%20counties.%20According%20to%20the%20government%2C%20the%20deadly%20wildfires%20have%20forced%20more%20than%2027%2C000%20residents%20to%20flee%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20videos%20were%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20showing%20firefighters%20trying%20to%20control%20the%20deadly%20blazes%20as%20strong%20winds%20and%20dry%20weather%20make%20their%20work%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAt%20least%2012%20dead%20in%20South%20Korea%20wildfires.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20massive%20forest%20fire%20that%20began%20in%20Uiseong%2C%20Gyeongbuk%2C%20has%20been%20spreading%20for%20four%20days%2C%20affecting%20Andong%2C%20Cheongsong%20Juwangsan%20National%20Park%2C%20Yeongyang%2C%20and%20Yeongdeok.%20The%20wildfire%20has%20resulted%20in%2012%20fatalities%2C%20with%20deaths%20reported%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FZ6U62BAXs3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FZ6U62BAXs3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Global%20Index%20(%40TheGlobal_Index)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheGlobal_Index%2Fstatus%2F1904644835124142152%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2025%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWildfires%20burning%20for%20a%20fifth-consecutive%20day%20in%20Ulsan%20and%20the%20Gyeongsang%20region%20are%20causing%20unprecedented%20damage%2C%26quot%3B%20South%20Korea's%20acting%20president%20Han%20Duck-soo%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20government%20has%20launched%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull-scale%20national%20response%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20government%20is%20deploying%20all%20available%20personnel%20and%20equipment%20in%20response%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bworst%20wildfires%20ever%2C%20but%20the%20situation%20is%20not%20good.%20Per%20the%20President%2C%20the%20US%20military%20in%20Korea%20was%20also%20assisting%20in%20firefighting%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20told%20an%20emergency%20safety%20and%20disaster%20meeting%20that%20the%20blazes%20were%20%26quot%3Bdeveloping%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20exceeding%20both%20existing%20prediction%20models%20and%20earlier%20expectations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20launched%20emergency%20evacuations%20on%20Tuesday%20afternoon%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20sadly%2C%20casualties%20could%20not%20be%20prevented%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThroughout%20the%20night%2C%20chaos%20continued%20as%20power%20and%20communication%20lines%20were%20cut%20in%20several%20areas%20and%20roads%20were%20blocked%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20firefighters%20have%20been%20deployed%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20winds%20reaching%20speeds%20of%2025%20metres%20per%20second%20persisted%20from%20yesterday%20afternoon%20through%20the%20night%2C%20forcing%20the%20suspension%20of%20helicopter%20and%20drone%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20Han%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConstantly%20shifting%20wind%20directions%20and%20ongoing%20dry%20weather%20advisories%20have%20revealed%20the%20limitations%20of%20conventional%20firefighting%20methods%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUNESCO-Listed%20Heritage%20Site%20Under%20Threat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blazes%20that%20broke%20out%20on%20Saturday%20in%20Uiseong%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20contained%20and%20are%20threatening%20several%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20sites%20-%20Hahoe%20Village%20and%20the%20Byeongsan%20Confucian%20Academy%20-%20in%20Andong%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20authorities%20issued%20an%20emergency%20alert%20for%20Hahoe%20Folk%20Village%20as%20the%20blaze%20drew%20closer.%20The%20flames%20had%20already%20burnt%20down%20Goun%20Temple%2C%20an%20ancient%20temple%20built%20in%20681%2C%20Yonhap%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20the%20blaze%20approaching%20the%20temple%20was%20shared%20on%20social%20media%2C%20which%20showed%20the%20people%20fleeing%20the%20premises%20before%20the%20flames%20engulfed%20the%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E1000%20year%20old%20Temple%20consumed%20by%20wildfire%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThousand-year-old%20Unramsa%20Temple%20on%20Cheondeungsan%20Mountain%20South%20Korea%2C%20was%20completely%20destroyed%20by%20a%20forest%20fire%20yesterday.%20It%20quickly%20spread%20due%20to%20strong%20winds%2C%20burning%20down%20both%20the%20main%20building%20and%20its%20outbuildings.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FX5Bk6aTjUy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FX5Bk6aTjUy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Volcaholic%20%F0%9F%8C%8B%20(%40volcaholic1)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fvolcaholic1%2Fstatus%2F1903760581015805987%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2023%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uiseong%20fire%2C%20only%2068%20per%20cent%20contained%20and%20exacerbated%20by%20gusty%20winds%2C%20shows%20%26quot%3Bunimaginable%26quot%3B%20scale%20and%20speed%2C%20said%20Lee%20Byung-doo%2C%20a%20forest%20disaster%20expert%20at%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Forest%20Science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20designated%20the%20affected%20areas%20as%20special%20disaster%20zones%2C%20and%20said%20the%20fires%20had%20damaged%20more%20than%2015%2C000%20hectares%20(37%2C065%20acres).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EClimate%20Change%20Behind%20Fires%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClimate%20change%20is%20projected%20to%20make%20wildfires%20more%20frequent%20globally%2C%20Lee%20said%2C%20citing%20the%20unusual%20timing%20of%20wildfires%20that%20ravaged%20part%20of%20Los%20Angeles%20in%20January%20and%20a%20recent%20wildfire%20in%20northeast%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20admit%20large-scale%20wildfires%20are%20going%20to%20increase%2C%20and%20for%20that%20we%20need%20more%20resources%20and%20trained%20manpower%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea%20relies%20on%20helicopters%20to%20help%20extinguish%20wildfires%20due%20to%20its%20mountainous%20terrain%2C%20but%20Lee%20said%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20bring%20in%20other%20fire-fighting%20aircraft%20and%20drones%20that%20can%20operate%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%20Russian%20helicopters%20out%20of%20the%20Korea%20Forest%20Service's%20fleet%20of%2048%20used%20in%20fire-fighting%20had%20been%20taken%20out%20of%20operation%20since%20last%20year%20due%20to%20an%20inability%20to%20import%20parts%20from%20Russia%20because%20of%20sanctions%20related%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20Yoon%20Joon-byeong%2C%20a%20Democratic%20Party%20lawmaker%20said%20in%20October%2C%20using%20data%20from%20the%20forest%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKim%20Jong-gun%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Korea%20Forest%20Service%2C%20said%20the%20agency%20planned%20to%20secure%20more%20wildfire-fighting%20helicopters%2C%20responding%20to%20criticism%20about%20a%20lack%20of%20equipment%20and%20helicopters%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%204%2C919%20firefighting%20personnel%20were%20being%20deployed%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20including%20hundreds%20of%20police%20officers%20and%20military%20units%2C%20while%2087%20helicopters%20were%20being%20used.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742967600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fl8vq0r48_south-korea-wildfire_625x300_26_Marc